m'hot undz arayngetribn, azoy vi in

00:11:57.685 --> 00:12:03.656
a ge- s'iz geven demls OBSHCHEZHITIE. azoy heyst OBSHCHEZHITIE, ()?

00:12:03.949 --> 00:12:07.051
s'iz geven z- mit di (laytsn), azoy ir hot gezen,

00:12:07.051 --> 00:12:09.782
di, di, di ge- lagers.

00:12:09.788 --> 00:12:14.996
ot dos, azoy hobn mir, in de- di mentshn vos m'hot genemen oyf der arbet...

00:12:15.019 --> 00:12:19.649
in geto iz geven a groyse shtub. s'hot a mol studentn geve-

00:12:19.649 --> 00:12:21.639
hobn zey dos farnemen far undz

00:12:21.639 --> 00:12:24.497
un m'hot gemakht (laytses) eyns oyfn andern,

00:12:24.503 --> 00:12:26.597
un azoy hobn mir, gelebt.

00:12:26.597 --> 00:12:29.505
dos glik iz geven vos mir hobn gehat a shtikl broyt

00:12:29.505 --> 00:12:31.754
un m'hot undz gegebn a bisl dort SUP.

00:12:31.945 --> 00:12:36.107
dos hobn, ho- hobn z-, hot undz geratevet biz tsun,

00:12:36.366 --> 00:12:39.431
biz tsun, fir un fertsikstn yor.

00:12:40.011 --> 00:12:43.835
fir un fertsikstn yor hot UNK, hot ongehoybn der rusisher

00:12:44.567 --> 00:12:48.189
zikh shlogn, er zol bafrayen di...

00:12:50.777 --> 00:12:52.856
iz,

00:12:53.528 --> 00:12:58.821
 ven m'hot ongehoybn bafrayen, dos iz, B-, BALTA hot men bafrayt,

00:12:59.603 --> 00:13:02.383
 hot men befray- bafrayt...

00:13:02.573 --> 00:13:04.676
dem bruder hot men derharget

00:13:04.699 --> 00:13:06.105
dray teg

00:13:06.105 --> 00:13:07.235
in IYAR.

00:13:07.235 --> 00:13:08.405
IYAR,

00:13:09.070 --> 00:13:11.882
der yidisher khoydesh, vayl ikh, ge-

00:13:12.192 --> 00:13:13.384
IYAR.

00:13:13.761 --> 00:13:17.981
dos iz, far, far pu- purim-peysekh. (IYAR).

00:13:19.701 --> 00:13:21.770
un dray teg befor

00:13:22.755 --> 00:13:27.503
m'hot, derharget dem bruder, nokh dray teg iz arayn, hot men undz bafrayt.

00:13:27.279 --> 00:13:28.661
ver hot im derharget?

00:13:27.503 --> 00:13:27.997
(z-)

00:13:28.527 --> 00:13:30.643
di daytshn, di esesovtses

00:13:30.643 --> 00:13:33.847
zenen arayngekumen (d-)... s'iz nisht nor bay undz in shtub.

00:13:33.893 --> 00:13:37.387
dos hot men aroysgenemen... ir zent dokh geven in der, in dem o...

00:13:37.387 --> 00:13:40.840
s'ershte hobn zey gegreykht tsu undz. m'hot aroysgenemen m- a-,

00:13:40.840 --> 00:13:42.730
m'hot aroysgenemen fun der shtub...

00:13:42.730 --> 00:13:44.467
zenen nor geblibn tsen mener,

00:13:44.507 --> 00:13:47.589
(nor meynstns iz) geven kinder mit, mit froyen.

00:13:47.967 --> 00:13:51.116
fun di tsen mener iz geven mayn bruder un mayn kuzin.

00:13:51.898 --> 00:13:53.114
ikh gedenk

00:13:53.114 --> 00:13:54.525
nokh tsvey mentshn:

00:13:55.527 --> 00:13:58.544
familye Vays, vos m'hot im geshosn.

00:13:58.544 --> 00:14:01.809
er hot zikh aropgev- er hot zikh aropge-

00:14:01.809 --> 00:14:05.893
un di K- di, KADUR- di, PULIs, di...

00:14:05.893 --> 00:14:07.316
zenen geblibn in im.

00:14:07.575 --> 00:14:08.868
un eyner

00:14:08.976 --> 00:14:10.758
iz gelofn, iz arayn,

00:14:10.832 --> 00:14:14.144
Shoy- Shoykhet, a bavuster,

00:14:14.144 --> 00:14:17.879
gevir fun (Bend), vos er iz geven mit undz. iz arayn in (Drubone).

00:14:18.088 --> 00:14:20.346
nokh dem hot er bakumen a,

00:14:20.346 --> 00:14:23.718
a in- a infektsye oyf di fis, m'hot im opgeshnitn.

00:14:23.995 --> 00:14:25.879
un (dos), di ershte,

00:14:25.952 --> 00:14:30.648
 ven der daytsh iz gekumen, hot gezogt, ar- aroysnemen di, di kinder,

00:14:30.648 --> 00:14:31.717
di mener,

00:14:32.314 --> 00:14:34.032
hot mayn mame im bahaltn.

00:14:34.032 --> 00:14:37.045
zi hot zikh aroyfgeleygt oyf im. zi hot aroyfgeleygt a,

00:14:37.045 --> 00:14:40.094
a koldre, a, a iberbet hobn mir nokh gehat,

00:14:40.094 --> 00:14:42.443
vos mir hobn zi geshlept dem gantsn veg.

00:14:42.443 --> 00:14:45.487
un UNK, un zi hot zikh aroyfgeleygt un ikh hob mikh aroyfgeleygt.

00:14:45.679 --> 00:14:50.485
un ven der esesovets hot gezogt, "ale d- ale yidn aroys, ale mener,

00:14:50.485 --> 00:14:52.940
un tomer nisht, vet zayn shlekht,"

00:14:52.940 --> 00:14:53.960
hot er (t-)

00:14:53.960 --> 00:14:57.913
iz geshtanen, der daytsh hot gezen, se tsitert epes unter der,

00:14:57.913 --> 00:14:59.865
unter der, iberbet.

00:15:00.428 --> 00:15:03.442
hot er, iz er aleyn aroys. zogt er, "dos bin ikh."

00:15:03.955 --> 00:15:10.173
un der shvesterkind un dortn di tsen mentshn fun undzer, hot men aroysgenemen.

00:15:10.452 --> 00:15:12.431
bin ikh nokhgelofn, vayl,

00:15:12.431 --> 00:15:14.191
bin nokhgelofn nokh im.

00:15:15.075 --> 00:15:20.216
un, v- un im hot men aroysgenemen oyf, in hoyf, in a groysn hoyf.

00:15:21.859 --> 00:15:28.755
ven er hot geshosn, hob ikh mikh aropgevorfn. (, d-) s'ershte vos kh'hob mikh aroy- vos ikh hob mir genemen in kop:

00:15:28.755 --> 00:15:31.286
vos (s'vet) nisht zayn, zol ikh mikh varfn oyf dr'erd.

00:15:31.815 --> 00:15:34.121
ven m'hot mikh s'ershte mol geshlogn,

00:15:34.498 --> 00:15:35.842
fun dem gold,

00:15:36.372 --> 00:15:41.884
hob ikh mikh, tseleygt un (zol) meynen az shoyn, s'iz, ikh bin, er zol mikh mer nit shlogn.

00:15:41.940 --> 00:15:43.891
un do hob ikh gevust az ikh...

00:15:44.185 --> 00:15:48.333
er hot gesh-, ikh hob mikh zofort aropgevorfn oyf dr'erd. er hot geshosn,

00:15:48.333 --> 00:15:50.181
zey hobn shoyn nisht gehat keyn tsayt.

00:15:50.181 --> 00:15:52.349
zey hobn oysgeshosn di,

00:15:52.349 --> 00:15:53.976
di ershte (g-)...

00:15:54.023 --> 00:15:57.949
ikh mit mayne oygn hob gezen vi m'hot geshosn di mentshn,

00:15:58.680 --> 00:16:02.448
un di ershte (ge-) PULIs, di ershte KADURIM

00:16:02.448 --> 00:16:04.102
iz arayn in mayn bruder

00:16:04.102 --> 00:16:05.998
un s'hot opgerisn a halbn kop.

00:16:06.021 --> 00:16:10.048
der halb-, mit di gehirn iz avek a halbn meter, nokh mer.

00:16:11.826 --> 00:16:13.154
(un) ikh hob gevart

00:16:13.154 --> 00:16:16.133
az zey zoln avekgeyn, di daytshn. m'hot nisht getort.

00:16:16.133 --> 00:16:17.607
in tsveytn tog

00:16:17.800 --> 00:16:21.273
hob ikh aroysgek- (u- u- un da-) hot er zikh umgekert,

00:16:21.580 --> 00:16:26.603
un er hot gevolt, er hot shoyn nisht gehat keyn tsayt undz tsu shisn, vayl er hot gedarft yedn oysshisn.

00:16:26.895 --> 00:16:28.779
hot er genemen a granate

00:16:28.870 --> 00:16:30.925
un er hot arayngevorfn... iz geven

00:16:30.925 --> 00:16:32.036
di tir,

00:16:32.262 --> 00:16:36.542
(vo-), akegn dem fentster, un di granate iz aroys,

00:16:36.733 --> 00:16:40.724
un, un a nes, s'iz aroys oyf der gas un mir zenen geblibn lebn.

00:16:43.753 --> 00:16:48.100
 tsishn di iz do a sakh mentshn vos ikh ken, vos zenen geblibn lebn,

00:16:48.546 --> 00:16:50.379
zenen do, lebn haynt,

00:16:51.533 --> 00:16:54.362
vos zey zenen geblibn lebn. nisht a sakh,

00:16:54.368 --> 00:16:58.723
nor s'iz nokh do mentshn vos zenen geblibn lebn.

00:16:59.920 --> 00:17:05.027
un az, in tsveytn tog bin ikh aroysgegangen, az mayn mame zol nisht zen

00:17:05.521 --> 00:17:07.598
dem groysn umglik, dem kop,

00:17:07.598 --> 00:17:09.560
a- er iz nishto (in halbn).

00:17:09.560 --> 00:17:11.253
hob ikh genemen a tikhl,

00:17:11.444 --> 00:17:14.138
ikh hob tsunoyfgenemen di gehirn mitn kop,

00:17:14.365 --> 00:17:16.062
ikh hob im ayn-....

00:17:16.930 --> 00:17:21.417
un di mame hot geshrign, gevolt ikh zol im araynnemen; er vet vern farfroyrn.

00:17:23.055 --> 00:17:25.597
kh'hob im gemuzt araynnemen. ikh hob gebetn mentshn.

00:17:25.637 --> 00:17:27.166
zi vil im onvaremen.

00:17:27.375 --> 00:17:30.426
nokh dem, ven di rusishe zenen shoyn arayngekumen,

00:17:30.426 --> 00:17:32.499
dos iz shoyn geven nokh dray teg.

00:17:33.045 --> 00:17:35.078
rusishe zenen arayngekumen,

00:17:36.866 --> 00:17:38.370
hot ongehoybn

00:17:38.370 --> 00:17:39.603
bombardirn.

00:17:40.690 --> 00:17:43.738
s'iz nokh nisht geven, s'iz nokh geven milkhome.

00:17:44.470 --> 00:17:46.421
ven ikh, m'hot aroysgetrogn...

00:17:46.849 --> 00:17:49.981
mir hobn aleyn im, bagrobn.

00:17:50.258 --> 00:17:51.689
mir hobn im aleyn.

00:17:51.689 --> 00:17:53.964
nokh dray teg iz shoyn geven di rusishe.

00:17:54.190 --> 00:17:57.626
hobn mir im genemen mit a leyter. vos hobn mir gekent tun?

00:17:58.003 --> 00:18:00.663
un ven mir hobn nor aroysgetrogn im

00:18:00.687 --> 00:18:02.014
oyf der leyter,

00:18:02.830 --> 00:18:09.610
(ho-) iz ongelofn di, di, (,) AVIRONIM, un s'iz gevorn a bom- bom- m-...

00:18:09.610 --> 00:18:11.368
dos iz geven,

00:18:11.368 --> 00:18:13.133
s'iz nisht tsu dertseyln (aykh).

00:18:13.242 --> 00:18:14.993
nor mir hobn im bagrobn.

00:18:14.993 --> 00:18:17.482
mir hobn dem kuzin oykh bagrobn in eynem.

00:18:17.482 --> 00:18:19.175
mir hobn gemakht a,

00:18:19.823 --> 00:18:22.255
a, beyde lign zey in eyn grub.

00:18:22.708 --> 00:18:24.063
oyfn yidishn,

00:18:24.063 --> 00:18:26.924
azoy vi mir zenen yidishe kinder, hobn mir gevolt

00:18:26.924 --> 00:18:30.380
az zey zoln vern bagrobn oyfn

00:18:30.123 --> 00:18:32.028
yidishn besoylem.

00:18:31.146 --> 00:18:33.789
yidishn besoylem, vu zey lign haynt.

00:18:34.588 --> 00:18:36.776
s'iz (dur-), mir hobn gezen

00:18:36.782 --> 00:18:39.189
az mir hobn nisht, (un vos zoln mir) tun do?

00:18:39.853 --> 00:18:43.216
hobn mir zikh tsunoyfgenemen etlekhe mentshn:

00:18:43.216 --> 00:18:46.833
ikh mit mayn, b- b- mit mayn mame,

00:18:47.042 --> 00:18:50.228
i- di tante mit ir kuzi- mit mayn kuzin,

00:18:50.228 --> 00:18:52.543
un nokh mentshn vos zenen gegangen, vos zenen nokh,

00:18:52.543 --> 00:18:56.026
nokh do di kinder fun zey, nokh (a) por mentshn vos zenen do.

00:18:56.026 --> 00:18:59.827
m'iz aroysgegangen dem ershtn may...dos vel ikh keyn mol nisht fargesn...

00:19:00.171 --> 00:19:01.380
tsu fus,

00:19:01.875 --> 00:19:03.502
dorf tsu dorf,

00:19:03.502 --> 00:19:09.058
shtetl tsu shtetl. (vif- v-) vu s'iz geven der front, vu (d-) s'iz geven der...

00:19:09.385 --> 00:19:11.618
hobn mir zikh opgeshtelt biz me nemt.

00:19:11.618 --> 00:19:14.694
mir hobn dokh nisht gekent, keyn Tshernovits hobn mir (nokh) nisht gekent geyn.

00:19:14.694 --> 00:19:16.807
Keshenev iz nokh nisht geven opgenumen.

00:19:16.807 --> 00:19:19.439
(zenen) mir gevoynt a bisl UNK in Belts.

00:19:19.439 --> 00:19:21.894
s'iz geven leydike shtiber, flegn mir arayngeyn.

00:19:21.894 --> 00:19:24.774
do hobn mir shoyn nisht moyre gehat, do zenen mir tsugegangen tsum feld.

00:19:24.774 --> 00:19:27.477
mir hobn genemen a shtikl, b-

00:19:27.477 --> 00:19:30.880
vos s'iz geven oyfn feld, zise burikes, dos...

00:19:30.880 --> 00:19:35.494
di goyim hobn a bisl gegebn. dos iz shoyn nisht geven...

00:19:35.494 --> 00:19:37.885
nor mir zenen gegangen tomed hintern front.

00:19:37.885 --> 00:19:42.801
vu m'hot opgenemen, dort, zenen mir, zenen mir gegangen, biz keyn Tshernovits.

00:19:42.814 --> 00:19:44.313
in Tshernovits

00:19:44.313 --> 00:19:46.200
zenen mir ongekumen...

00:19:46.932 --> 00:19:50.472
ikh ken nisht ge- gedenken vifl es hot gedoyert der veg,

00:19:50.472 --> 00:19:52.174
nor s'hot gedoyert a sakh,

00:19:52.483 --> 00:19:53.889
vayl,

00:19:53.889 --> 00:19:56.176
 s'iz nokh nisht (Keshe-) mir hobn gedarft geyn

00:19:56.176 --> 00:19:58.690
durkh Belts, durkh Keshenev, UNK hobn mir...

00:19:58.690 --> 00:20:02.617
iz umedum iz geven di b- hobn mir d- zenen mir geven hinter der,

00:20:02.617 --> 00:20:04.847
dort hot men bombardirt, dort hot men geshlogn,

00:20:04.847 --> 00:20:06.891
nor mir hobn nisht gehat keyn andern veg. me hot,

00:20:06.891 --> 00:20:09.489
m'iz gegangen. vos hot men gehat tsu trakhtn?

00:20:09.489 --> 00:20:11.727
mir hobn shoyn nisht getrakht fun undzer lebn. az me,

00:20:11.727 --> 00:20:13.122
mir hobn gezen a shtub,

00:20:13.122 --> 00:20:14.398
zenen mir arayngegangen.

00:20:14.792 --> 00:20:16.828
mir hobn zikh avekge-

00:20:17.020 --> 00:20:20.375
 m'iz gegangen betn a shtikl broyt bay di goyim.

00:20:20.375 --> 00:20:22.692
m- s'i- mir hobn shoyn UNK.

00:20:22.692 --> 00:20:24.281
dos iz geven undzer lebn.

00:20:24.281 --> 00:20:25.569
un nokh dem,

00:20:25.828 --> 00:20:29.462
bin ongekumen keyn Tshernovits, hot men undz nisht arayngelozt keyn Tshernovits.

00:20:29.462 --> 00:20:31.538
m'hot gegebn a bafel

00:20:31.538 --> 00:20:33.450
az mir zenen farlayzikt

00:20:33.743 --> 00:20:35.068
un mit krank.

00:20:35.068 --> 00:20:37.365
hot men undz nisht arayngelozt in Tshernovits.

00:20:37.894 --> 00:20:39.643
hot men undz opgehaltn

00:20:40.020 --> 00:20:41.229
bay der brik.

00:20:41.944 --> 00:20:45.222
(nu), di, (min-) in, mit, zek, (kl-)

00:20:45.222 --> 00:20:50.156
UNK, far, m'hot undz gegebn a kuk on, hot men undz nisht. nor mir kinder, ikh mit mayn kuzin,

00:20:50.803 --> 00:20:55.353
s- mayn tante... s'iz geven a tante mayne, vos zi hot zikh gefunen in geto;

00:20:55.444 --> 00:20:57.348
ir man iz geven

00:20:57.348 --> 00:20:58.796
a spetsyalist

00:20:59.055 --> 00:21:00.300
inzhenyer,

00:21:00.300 --> 00:21:01.829
un ir eydem oykh.

00:21:01.829 --> 00:21:05.186
hot men im gel- iz er geblibn in geto, un er hot gearbet;

00:21:05.186 --> 00:21:09.022
zey hobn gedarft im hobn. hot er gearbet, nor er iz geven in geto.

00:21:09.990 --> 00:21:13.730
hobn mir gevust az zey gef- az zey zenen dort, un kinder.

00:21:13.990 --> 00:21:18.557
vu hobn mir nisht gevust; mir hobn nor gevust vu dos geto iz. hobn mir ongehoybn zukhn.

00:21:19.002 --> 00:21:24.761
hobn mir di mame mit, mit der tante ibergelozt un mir zenen gegangen zukhn di, di,

00:21:24.761 --> 00:21:28.783
di, di shvester fun der mame mit der mishpokhe, di vos iz do.

00:21:29.059 --> 00:21:34.892
zenen mir, m- un mir hobn zey getrofn. azoy hobn mir zey getrofn? mir hobn gevust az der onkl

00:21:35.185 --> 00:21:41.649
iz a groyser, mentsh in der fabrik un z- a guter spetsyalist. er iz geven a guter,...

00:21:41.649 --> 00:21:45.636
zenen mir arayngegangen in der fabrik. mir hobn, mir zenen dokh, gevust vu er (g-) hot gearbet,

00:21:45.789 --> 00:21:49.152
in der spirt-, -fabrik, un s'iz geven nokh a fabrik.

00:21:49.427 --> 00:21:55.597
un mir hobn gefregt, di familye. hot men... un er iz zofort (s-) er hot gemeynt az mir zenen shoyn nishto.

00:21:57.072 --> 00:22:01.959
un, hot er, gezogt, hot er undz derzen,

00:22:02.455 --> 00:22:05.132
un er hot gezogt, "veyst vos, (ts-) ir geyt durkh

00:22:05.205 --> 00:22:07.395
un ikh'l makhn shoyn papirn,

00:22:07.395 --> 00:22:10.551
az ikh zol kenen di mame, tsukumen tsu der mame,

00:22:10.551 --> 00:22:13.317
(ikh) zol kenen di mame tsunemen (mi-)",

00:22:13.317 --> 00:22:15.866
(vayl) m'hot nisht getort arayngeyn in der shtot.

00:22:16.309 --> 00:22:19.880
un mir zenen dervayl (g-) ge- shoyn gehat den adres fun der mume,

00:22:20.376 --> 00:22:22.968
un mir zenen gekumen t- arayn

00:22:22.975 --> 00:22:26.060
tsu ir. mir hobn zi getrofn, un zi hot undz derzen,

00:22:26.060 --> 00:22:27.880
iz gevorn groyse gevaldn,

00:22:28.054 --> 00:22:30.438
vayl zi hot gevust, mir zenen, keyner iz nishto.

00:22:30.438 --> 00:22:37.700
un do hot zi gevust az tsvey kinder iz gekumen, iz shoyn nishto di shvestern oykh nisht, keyner, nor mir zenen geblibn.

00:22:37.926 --> 00:22:42.395
zi hot gekhalesht oyfn plats. nokh dem hot der onkl ongeklungen mit dem o,

00:22:42.395 --> 00:22:43.947
az dem, di,

00:22:43.947 --> 00:22:47.378
er kumt bald mit, der mame un mit der tante.

00:22:48.338 --> 00:22:51.386
un mir hobn zikh umgek- dos iz shoyn geven...

00:22:51.966 --> 00:22:54.660
mir, di shtiber iz geven leydike.

00:22:54.936 --> 00:22:58.457
dort vu mir hobn gevoynt hobn mir shoyn nisht gekent, voynen.

00:22:58.986 --> 00:23:04.447
hobn mir zikh, aranzhirt, in a shtub (t-) a leydikn arayngegangen, dos iz geven.

00:23:05.668 --> 00:23:08.618
mayn mame iz nisht geven shoyn keyn mentsh.

00:23:08.618 --> 00:23:10.404
ikh bin geblibn a kind.

00:23:10.579 --> 00:23:12.069
hob gedarft zayn

00:23:12.069 --> 00:23:13.559
i broyt-geber

00:23:13.988 --> 00:23:16.583
i,

00:23:16.583 --> 00:23:18.218
ales bin ikh geven.

00:23:19.050 --> 00:23:22.943
kh'hob gedarft di mame hodeven un ales, ikh mit...

00:23:22.943 --> 00:23:24.748
dos bin ikh geven mit der mame.

00:23:25.446 --> 00:23:29.625
nor ikh bin nisht geven farshlofn. ikh bin tomed geven a tikhtik kind.

00:23:30.340 --> 00:23:34.249
un, ikh bin, un ikh hob ge- s'hot mikh getrogn der kop.

00:23:34.575 --> 00:23:36.002
fleg ikh, (kh'hob dokh)

00:23:36.002 --> 00:23:37.753
gevolt shtark lernen,

00:23:37.753 --> 00:23:40.442
vayl mir zenen geven fun a shtub...

00:23:40.937 --> 00:23:45.150
hob ikh gezogt, ikh'l geyn oyf der nakht lernen, un bay tog

00:23:45.493 --> 00:23:48.440
vel ikh ales tun, az ikh zol haltn mayn mame.

00:23:49.138 --> 00:23:51.528
hob ikh mikh s'ershte aranzhirt,

00:23:51.805 --> 00:23:55.202
bay tsvey balebatim bin ikh arayngegangen. s'iz geven in a,

00:23:55.202 --> 00:23:57.244
a magazin fun,

00:23:57.244 --> 00:23:58.231
fun esn.

00:23:58.231 --> 00:24:00.366
dos hot es geheysn, azoy vi a,

00:24:00.366 --> 00:24:03.454
 SUPER, ABER a kleyner SUPER.

00:24:04.545 --> 00:24:07.692
bin ikh arayngegangen. kh'hob mir gebetn oyf arbet.

00:24:08.106 --> 00:24:12.470
zogt er, "nu, prubi- shtel zikh avek, veln mir zen oyb du kenst arbetn."

00:24:12.510 --> 00:24:14.313
iz er hot ge- zofort gezen...

00:24:14.313 --> 00:24:18.242
bay undz iz dokh geven a kleyt un aldings un ikh bin geven...

00:24:18.366 --> 00:24:20.658
zogt er, "blaybst bay mir arbetn."

00:24:20.880 --> 00:24:23.640
zog ikh, "ABER s'vet mir nisht zayn genug der,

00:24:23.640 --> 00:24:26.724
der loyn vos ikh'l bakumen. ikh hob a mame,

00:24:26.724 --> 00:24:28.141
vos (vet), vos...

00:24:28.141 --> 00:24:30.892
far mir vi far mir, ABER ikh darf hobn di mame.

00:24:30.892 --> 00:24:33.659
kh'hob nisht keyn shikh. kh'hob nisht keyn kleyd.

00:24:33.659 --> 00:24:36.466
kh'hob gornisht un ikh darf ontun i di mame i mikh."

00:24:37.924 --> 00:24:39.836
zogt er, "veys vos?

00:24:39.836 --> 00:24:42.681
ikh'l dir gebn a por mentsh-, por shtiber,

00:24:42.681 --> 00:24:44.941
bay mayn froy, bay nokh emetser,

00:24:44.941 --> 00:24:47.756
vestu vashn vesh, vestu presn,

00:24:47.762 --> 00:24:49.936
vestu tun di zakhn oykhet."

00:24:50.074 --> 00:24:52.025
bin ikh oykh maskem geven.

00:24:52.032 --> 00:24:54.489
fleg ikh vashn dortn, mit di hent.

00:24:55.221 --> 00:24:59.366
un, zi hot mir gegebn esn. zog ikh, "ir veyst vos? (ir vet mir gebn)

00:24:59.878 --> 00:25:04.330
 veyniker a bisl, un lozt mir dos bisl; ikh darf trogn mayn mame esn."

00:25:04.330 --> 00:25:06.322
in tsayt fleg ikh antloyfn

00:25:06.322 --> 00:25:08.040
un gebn mayn mame dos esn.

00:25:08.991 --> 00:25:11.044
un oyf der nakht fleg ikh geyn lernen.

00:25:11.657 --> 00:25:16.156
ikh, mayn mame hot, in fertsikstn yor, hob ikh aykh fargesn tsu zogn,

00:25:16.416 --> 00:25:18.536
az mir zenen gekumen ahin tsu,

00:25:18.964 --> 00:25:20.732
hot di mame shtark gevolt,

00:25:20.732 --> 00:25:22.889
ikh zol geyn in a yidisher shul.

00:25:23.892 --> 00:25:28.343
un in k- un in fertsikstn yor, biz tsun akht un fertsikstn yor,

00:25:28.343 --> 00:25:34.634
iz nokh geven in Rusland yidishe kultur, yidishe...

00:25:35.957 --> 00:25:37.351
bin ikh gegangen,

00:25:37.763 --> 00:25:42.448
biz tsu der milkhome, biz tsu geto un ales, bin ikh gegangen in a yidisher shul.

00:25:43.180 --> 00:25:44.999
un az ikh bin tsurikgekumen,

00:25:44.999 --> 00:25:48.928
hob ikh gevolt vider dos yidishe, az s'iz do a yidishe shul,

00:25:49.120 --> 00:25:51.274
hob ikh geendikt di yidishe shul.

00:25:51.955 --> 00:25:54.936
un bay undz, nokh, akht klasn,

00:25:55.971 --> 00:25:58.467
hob ikh gekent, vayter lernen.

00:25:58.467 --> 00:26:01.078
dos iz geven oykh, demls in yene tsaytn.	

00:26:02.181 --> 00:26:04.000
un ikh bin gegangen

00:26:04.000 --> 00:26:04.993
arbetn

00:26:05.893 --> 00:26:10.302
in a, TRI- T- TRIKOTAZHNYY TRINAKO fabrik,

00:26:11.074 --> 00:26:14.928
vu ikh z- vu ikh hob gelernt i gearbet.

00:26:15.073 --> 00:26:17.072
gelernt un gearbet.

00:26:17.470 --> 00:26:19.877
dos hob ikh shoyn gehat i praktike

00:26:20.068 --> 00:26:21.091
i...

00:26:21.199 --> 00:26:23.507
nokh dem hob ikh bakumen

00:26:23.507 --> 00:26:25.338
a, mayn arbet.

00:26:25.338 --> 00:26:26.644
ikh bin geven,

00:26:27.493 --> 00:26:31.798
oyf rusish hot dos geheysn NACHAL'NIK (UNK)KA,

00:26:31.881 --> 00:26:34.136
 MENAHELET BIKORET.

00:26:34.291 --> 00:26:37.210
hob ikh bakumen tekhnolog, (ikh bin,)

00:26:37.210 --> 00:26:38.560
MENAHEL BIKORET

00:26:38.560 --> 00:26:40.177
fun dray hundert mentshn.

00:26:42.107 --> 00:26:45.094
un kh'hob gearbet, yo,

00:26:45.094 --> 00:26:46.775
dos iz,

00:26:47.322 --> 00:26:50.117
dos mey- mayne meydlshe yorn

00:26:50.798 --> 00:26:54.101
hob ikh geendikt un ikh hob mikh bagegnt...

00:26:54.101 --> 00:26:58.571
 ikh, (oh)... mayn mame hob ikh shoyn a bisl geshtelt oyf di fis.

00:26:58.780 --> 00:27:00.346
kh'hob zi ongetun.

00:27:00.346 --> 00:27:03.499
kh'hob s'ershte zi ongetun un nokh dem mikh.

00:27:03.724 --> 00:27:11.143
m- mir, hobn shoyn gekoy-, mir hobn shoyn gehat a bisl zakhn, a dank mir, vos ikh hob gedarft ales,...

00:27:12.178 --> 00:27:15.682
hob ikh zi geshtelt a bisl oyf di fis

00:27:15.840 --> 00:27:20.216
un zi hot op- z- un ikh hob zi aranzhirt, vayl zi iz geven zeyer a feike.

00:27:20.216 --> 00:27:21.866
hot zi gearbet

00:27:21.866 --> 00:27:23.211
a k-,

00:27:23.211 --> 00:27:26.178
UNK MENAHELET,

00:27:26.438 --> 00:27:27.664
a kikh.

00:27:27.923 --> 00:27:30.026
nor nisht a stam a kikh,

00:27:31.399 --> 00:27:32.729
fun di HANHALA.

00:27:32.729 --> 00:27:34.369
fun di gr(UNK).

00:27:34.943 --> 00:27:38.480
un dortn hot zi opgearbet

00:27:39.330 --> 00:27:40.691
nisht lang,

00:27:42.739 --> 00:27:46.901
un zi hot nisht gekent, merer arbetn,

00:27:47.903 --> 00:27:51.658
un... hob ikh, gevolt zi zol khasene hobn,

00:27:52.003 --> 00:27:53.072
vayl

00:27:53.072 --> 00:27:55.390
zi iz geven etlekhe un draysik yor.

00:27:56.037 --> 00:28:00.300
az kh'hob zi shoyn geshtelt oyfn veg, hob ikh gezogt, zi zol khasene hobn,

00:28:00.424 --> 00:28:01.936
vayl ikh,

00:28:03.040 --> 00:28:05.869
UNK ikh bin shoyn oykh gevorn a...

00:28:06.330 --> 00:28:08.771
hob ikh gen- hob ikh getrakht azoy.

00:28:08.946 --> 00:28:16.449
ikh vil zi zen far a baleboste. az zi vet zayn a baleboste, vel ikh, nokh dem ken ikh khasene hobn. un far vos darf zi bay etlekhe un draysik yor

00:28:16.472 --> 00:28:24.110
nisht zayn... a sheyne froy, a ge- a gelernte, a gebildete froy. kh'hob gelebt far ir, az zi zol...

00:28:24.572 --> 00:28:26.608
V OBSHCHEM zi hot khasene gehat.

00:28:26.867 --> 00:28:29.392
zi hot khasene gehat, ABER ikh

00:28:29.820 --> 00:28:31.602
bin mir geven ma- aleyn.

00:28:32.554 --> 00:28:36.091
vos heyst aleyn? kh'bin geven in shtub, ABER

00:28:36.250 --> 00:28:38.068
ikh hob gefirt

00:28:38.173 --> 00:28:40.951
(a s-, ATS-) ATSMAI(T) lebn.

00:28:41.025 --> 00:28:43.274
ikh bin tsu keynem nisht ongekumen.

00:28:43.274 --> 00:28:44.849
ikh hob fardint.

00:28:45.042 --> 00:28:46.931
ikh bin geven...

00:28:47.202 --> 00:28:52.978
un bin gegangen... di meydlekh hobn mikh gerufn, "kum a bisl shpatsirn." s'iz mir nisht geven in kop.

00:28:52.978 --> 00:28:56.462
un bin aroysgegangen eyn mol fun der shtub,

00:28:56.462 --> 00:29:03.727
un zey hobn mikh farnemen oyf, "kum, dort iz do a yidishe kompanye. far vos darfstu zayn azoy o?"

00:29:03.727 --> 00:29:06.532
un dos ershte mol vos ikh bin aroysgegangen,

00:29:06.532 --> 00:29:08.228
hob ikh bagegnt mayn man.